text.paragraph:
The maximum single recommended dose of Sumavel DosePro for the acute treatment of migraine or cluster headache is 6 mg given subcutaneously. For the treatment of migraine, if side effects are dose limiting, a lower dose (4 mg) may be used [see 
                           Clinical Studies (

                              14.1

                           )
                           ]. For the treatment of cluster headache, the efficacy of a lower dose has not been established.

